headline: Q4 Earnings Recap: Lindsay (NYSE:LNN) Tops Agricultural Machinery Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at agricultural machinery stocks, starting with Lindsay (NYSE:LNN).
